reviews.comment:
(Translated by Google) The frankfurter is fine, the food acceptable but I can't understand how if I ask for bread with tomato for my omelette they charge me 0.75 extra. I understand the extra cheese, but each sandwich we ordered with tomato breadcrumbs was 0.75... I had never been charged for it in any bar. Here I leave my complaint.

(Original)
El frankfurt esta bien, la comida aceptable pero no puedo entender como si pido pan con tomate  para mi tortilla me cobren 0,75 de suplemento. Del queso extra lo entiendo pero cada bocadillo que pedimos con pan rallado de tomate 0,75..nunca me lo habian cobrado en ningun bar. Aqui os dejo mi queja.
